headline.main: Failure at Moscow a Psychological Blow -- Neutrality Act Upset Another Setback

lead_paragraph: WASHINGTON, Nov. 18 -- As the Germans started a new and possibly abortive offensive against Moscow yesterday, the Russian campaign -- and the war kaleidoscope -- completed another phase.
abstract: H W Baldwin on German failure in Moscow drive
